snippet.title: Version 4.6 "Two Worlds Aflame, the Crimson Night Fades" Trailer | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
All plans need someone to enact them.
May frost blush under the crimson moon,
A symphony resound from the depths,
And let sandswept secrets sleep no more,
Til there's naught but to await an inescapable fate.

VA:
"The Knave" Arlecchino — Erin Yvette
Alhaitham — Nazeeh H. Tarsha
Cyno — Alejandro Saab
"Childe" Tartaglia — Griffin Burns
Lyney — Daman Mills
Neuvillette — Ray Chase
Freminet — Paul Castro Jr.
Sethos — Zeno Robinson
Arataki Itto — Max Mittelman
Paimon — Corina Boettger
